Crisply,is,a,time,tracking,service,that,connects,with,other,systems,used,to,automatically,track,a,user,s,time,Some,features,of,Crisply,include,timesheets,project,systems,and,billing,systems,The,Crisply,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Crisply,with,other,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,accessing,timesheets,retrieving,times,logged,by,activity,and,client,and,managing,user,information,and,account,information